{
  "stem": "19055.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was quite successful at this, I don't have to say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The superficial elements, the, the nobodies, the no goods immediately joined the party.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they, they cherished their uniforms, their-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the black ties and, and the green shirts, and, and the bands.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were roaming the streets sometimes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His-- this teacher was actually my fencing teacher, given at early age.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] his son was very little, maybe five years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He, he would walk on the street with a whip.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he knew who we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody knew who we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody knew who was Jewish, who wasn't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he would meet me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would raise his hand-- the five-year-old child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he'd whip me with the whip.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- and he would-- he could hardly say Jew-- Jid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He would say, 'Jid, Jid, Jid.' What can you do with a child like this, you know, where he came from?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So finally, when I went to high school, this Koppanyi was our gym teacher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was an anecdote that I have to tell you, because it's still in my mind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I see the picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was an Olympic fencer, a Jewish man, whose name was John Schporer, a tall, lean man, a wonderful person, who was my English teacher when I was nine years old.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents hired him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this Nazi, Koppanyi, he liked to fence very much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he would invite Schporer to fence with him, in spite of he being a Jew and this guy was a-- the head of the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would sit down in the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were watching these two men fence. the-- with sword.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had their white outfits and the mask.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
